Title: Go Figure
Actors: Jordan Danger, Whitney Sloan, Cristine Rose, Ryan Malgarini
Plot: "Go Figure" follows 14-year-old Katelin in her quest to become a world class championship ice skater. When renowned Russian figure skating coach Natasha Goberman offers to train her at the private school where she teaches, Katelin will do almost anything to take advantage of the opportunity - even join the girl's hockey team on scholarship.
Production: Disney Channel, Salty Features, Just Singer Entertainment
